# 1949 Rutgers Queensmen football team

The 1949 Rutgers Queensmen football team represented Rutgers University in the 1949 college football season. In their eighth season under head coach Harvey Harman, the Queensmen compiled a 6â€“3 record, won the Middle Three Conference championship, and outscored their opponents 266 to 138.
